B・W"]},{"attributes":["Slash"],"block_number":3,"category":"Character","colors":["Blue"],"cost":4,"counter":1000,"effect":"【啟動主要】可以廢棄1張自己的手牌、將這張角色卡放置在廢棄區：若自己的領航卡是「巴其」時，使最多1張自己手牌中費用6以下擁有《十字公會》特徵的角色卡登場。","id":"ST25-004","img_full_url":"https://asia-tw.onepiece-cardgame.com/images/cardlist/card/ST25-004.png?260629","img_url":"../images/cardlist/card/ST25-004.png?260629","name":"巴其","pack_id":"554025","power":1000,"rarity":"SuperRare","trigger":null,"types":["四皇","十字公會"]},{"attributes":["Wisdom"],"block_number":3,"category":"Character","colors":["Blue"],"cost":4,"counter":2000,"effect":"若場上有2張以上自己原本費用5以上的角色卡時，這張角色卡獲得【防禦】、費用+1。<br>(對手攻擊後，將這張卡片置為休息狀態即可使攻擊的對象換成這張卡片)<br>【KO時】若自己的領航卡是「巴其」、自己的手牌在3張以下時，抽1張卡片。","id":"ST25-005","img_full_url":"https://asia-tw.onepiece-cardgame.com/images/cardlist/card/ST25-005.png?260629","img_url":"../images/cardlist/card/ST25-005.png?260629","name":"摩奇","pack_id":"554025","power":1000,"rarity":"Common","trigger":null,"types":["十字公會"]}]